Advantage of Inoue balloon catheter in mitral balloon valvotomy: experience with 220 consecutive patients. Percutaneous mitral balloon valvotomy (PMV) using the Inoue balloon catheter was attempted in 220 consecutive patients with severe symptomatic mitral stenosis. Their age range was 10-63 mean 30 +/- 10 years 161 patients were females and 59 were males